'''泉'''（{{lang-fr|'''''La Source'''''}}）是[[法国|法国]]画家[[让·奥古斯特·多米尼克·安格尔|让·奥古斯特·多米尼克·安格尔]]于1856年创作的一幅[[油画|油画]]。现藏于法国[[巴黎|巴黎]]的[[奧塞博物館|奧塞博物館]]。画家1820年在[[佛罗伦萨|佛罗伦萨]]时就开始绘制这幅作品了，直到1856年76岁时才完成<ref name="Musée d'Orsay">{{cite web |url=http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?no_cache=1&nnumid=525 |title=La Source |publisher=[[Musée_d'Orsay|Musée d'Orsay]] |accessdate=2 March 2012 |archive-date=2018-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625132810/http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des-oeuvres/notice.html?no_cache=1&nnumid=525 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Company2003">{{cite book |author=Houghton Mifflin Company |title=The Houghton Mifflin dictionary of biography |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rySr84jox_AC&pg=PA782 |year=2003 |publisher=[[Houghton_Mifflin_Harcourt|Houghton Mifflin Harcourt]] |isbn=978-0-618-25210-7 |pages=782- |access-date=2018-11-21 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324124836/https://books.google.com/books?id=rySr84jox_AC&pg=PA782 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Arnheim2004">{{cite book |author=Arnheim, Rudolf |title=Art and visual perception: a psychology of the creative eye |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9RktoatXGQ0C&pg=PA152 |year=2004 |publisher=[[University_of_California_Press|University of California Press]] |isbn=978-0-520-24383-5 |page=152 |access-date=2018-11-21 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324124800/https://books.google.com/books?id=9RktoatXGQ0C&pg=PA152 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

画中少女全裸伫立，手捧水罐。朝下的罐口流淌着清水。少女的身体丰满细润，面容悠闲端庄，处处散发着青春的气息和生命的活力。

